#-  §2 §r§l§2   Teachings§r


§l§0The Teachings of the Roots:§r

Your connection to the world and its riches are strong and sturdy. Lose touch with those around you and you will fall.
#-  §2 §r§l§2 The Teachings§r


§l§0The Teachings of the Bark:§r

Remain resolute in the face of danger and never give an inch to those who seek to harm. Surrender is abhorrent.
#-  §2 §r§l§2 The Teachings§r


§l§0The Teachings of the Leaves:§r

You may fall. If you do, fall gracefully. Rely on the Bark and the Roots and the leaves will regrow.
